These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | juice | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, engineer
1. the videographer is on the left or right of the engineer##3
2. the engineer is on the right of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | videographer | engineer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | cooking | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | funk |

 #################################

 
